quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  93,1,(I swear) by the morning light
  93,2,"And the night, as it becomes calm"
  93,3,"(Oh Muhammad, SAW), your Lord has not forsaken you; He is not displeased"
  93,4,The life to come is better for you than the earlier life
  93,5,"Soon, your Lord will grant you (His blessings); you shall be well-pleased"
  93,6,"Did He not find you an orphan, and gave you shelter"
  93,7,"He found you unguided, and guided you"
  93,8,"Found you poor, and enriched you"
  93,9,So do not oppress the orphan
  93,10,"And do not (angrily) repulse (and rebuff) the needy, the beggar"
  93,11,"(Rather), proclaim the favors of your Lord"